Package: aire.zmvm
Type: Package
Title: Download pollution data for the Zona Metropolitana del Valle de Mexico
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Diego Valle-Jones
Maintainer: Diego Valle-Jones <diego@diegovalle.net>
Description: This package can download the daily maximum, minimum, or hourly average for each
    of the pollution measuring stations or zones in the Zona Metropolitana del Valle de Mexico.
    It also contains the locations of each of the stations.
License: BSD_3_clause + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
